  "local_port": 41844,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some of the websites similar to carrierbuilder.com?",
  "response": "It appears you may be referring to **CareerBuilder.com**, a well-known job search and career development platform. If that's the case, here are several websites similar to CareerBuilder that can help you with job searching, career advice, and professional networking:\n\n1. **[Indeed](https://www.indeed.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** One of the largest job search engines worldwide, aggregating listings from thousands of websites, including company career pages and job boards.\n   - **Features:** Job alerts, company reviews, salary information, and resume posting.\n\n2. **[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** A professional networking platform that also offers extensive job listings.\n   - **Features:** Networking opportunities, professional profiles, industry news, and job recommendations based on your profile.\n\n3. **[Monster](https://www.monster.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** A long-established job board offering a wide range of job listings across various industries.\n   - **Features:** Resume building, career advice, job alerts, and company profiles.\n\n4. **[Glassdoor](https://www.glassdoor.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** Combines job listings with company reviews and salary information provided by employees.\n   - **Features:** Company insights, interview reviews, salary estimates, and job postings.\n\n5. **[SimplyHired](https://www.simplyhired.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** A job search engine that aggregates listings from all over the web, including company sites and job boards.\n   - **Features:** Salary estimator, job trends, and localized job listings.\n\n6. **[ZipRecruiter](https://www.ziprecruiter.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** Connects employers with job seekers through a large network of job boards.\n   - **Features:** Job matching, resume database access for employers, and mobile-friendly application process.\n\n7. **[Dice](https://www.dice.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** Specializes in technology and IT job listings.\n   - **Features:** Tech-focused job postings, career advice for tech professionals, and skill assessments.\n\n8. **[Snagajob](https://www.snagajob.com/)**\n   - **Overview:** Focuses on hourly and part-time jobs across various industries.\n   - **Features:** Real-time job alerts, shift scheduling tools, and employer profiles.\n\n9. **[AngelList](https://angel.co/)**\n   - **Overview:** A platform for startups to post job listings and connect with potential employees.\n   - **Features:** Startup-focused opportunities, company insights, and the ability to apply privately.\n\n10. **[FlexJobs](https://www.flexjobs.com/)**\n    - **Overview:** Specializes in remote, part-time, freelance, and flexible job opportunities.\n    - **Features:** Hand-screened job listings, career coaching, and skills tests.\n\n11. **[Jobs.com](https://www.jobs.com/)**\n    - **Overview:** Offers job listings along with career resources and a resume builder.\n    - **Features:** Job search tools, career advice articles, and application tracking.\n\n12. **[Ladders](https://www.theladders.com/)**\n    - **Overview:** Focuses on high-paying jobs, typically requiring six-figure salaries.\n    - **Features:** Executive job listings, career advice, and networking opportunities.\n\nIf you were indeed referring to a different website, such as **CarrierBuilder.com**, which might be related to a specific industry like transportation or telecommunications, please provide more details. This will help in offering more accurate alternatives tailored to that field.",
